          <h3 className="text-xl font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-2">
            姝ｅ湪鎵归噺鐢熸垚璧勬簮...
          </h3>
          <div className="w-64 h-1.5 bg-[var(--bg-hover)] rounded-full overflow-hidden mb-2">
            <div
